=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Types<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Cholesterol <\/strong>Polyp (Most Common)<\/li><li>Inflammatory<\/li><li>Adenoma<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Malignancy Risk Factors<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Size<ul><li>&gt; 1 cm (43-77% Risk)<\/li><li>&gt; 2 cm (Nearly 100% Risk)<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Age &gt; 50<\/li><li>Associated Gallstones<\/li><li>Solitary Polyp (vs Multiple)<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Diagnosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Often Identified on US<\/li><li>Should be Evaluated with CT or MRI<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>&lt; 1 cm &amp; ASx: <strong>Monitor with US<\/strong><ul><li>Cholecystectomy if: <strong>PSC\/UC<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><strong>&gt; 1 cm<\/strong> or Sx: Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy<ul><li>If &gt; 2 cm: Consider Extended Cholecystectomy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-19c5785\" data-id=\"19c5785\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55b99b3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"55b99b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10252 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gallbladder-Polyp.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gallbladder-Polyp.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Gallbladder-Polyp-300x223.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Gallbladder Polyp on US <sup>3<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5fb86c4 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5fb86c4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-fcbf15c\" data-id=\"fcbf15c\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-825fe9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"825fe9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Gallbladder Adenocarcinoma<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2b32976 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2b32976\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container element